---

<section
  class="relative h-full w-full flex items-center overflow-hidden lg:py-40 pt-28 pb-10"
>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
    <img
      src="/images/logo.png"
      alt="Legal Team Background"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-20"
    />
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-background via-background/60 to-transparent"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto w-full px-8">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] relative">
      <h1
        class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-[1.1] mb-8 animate-up"
      >
        El Equipo de Defensa Legal <br />
        <span class="text-primary italic font-serif"
          >Que Usted Realmente Merece</span
        >
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-[1.1rem] md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-gray-600 mb-10 max-w-[600px] animate-up delay-100"
      >
        Expertos en leyes de quiebra dedicados a proteger su patrimonio y
        brindarle la tranquilidad financiera que su familia necesita. Un nuevo
        comienzo es posible.
      </p>

      <div class="animate-up delay-200">
        <a
          href="#contacto"
          class="inline-block bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white px-11 py-5 rounded-sm font-bold text-base uppercase tracking-widest transition-all hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-2xl"
        >
          Solicitar Consulta
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .animate-up {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
    }

    .delay-100 {
      animation-delay: 0.2s;
    }
    .delay-200 {
      animation-delay: 0.4s;
    }
    .delay-300 {
      animation-delay: 0.6s;
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
  </style>
</section>
